00:23:33.000 --> 00:23:35.000
this well-known spot in 

00:23:35.000 --> 00:23:38.000
the 3rd movement of Rimsky-Korsakov's Scheherezade - which, as 

00:23:38.000 --> 00:23:49.000
you know, is madly Oriental:

00:23:49.000 --> 00:23:52.000
