00:25:09.000 --> 00:25:11.000
you can tell me. I'm going to play you our 

00:25:11.000 --> 00:25:16.000
normal scale of F major, and now, the

00:25:16.000 --> 00:25:21.000
Lydian scale starting on F. 

00:25:21.000 --> 00:25:23.000
Now there's one very peculiar note in that 

00:25:23.000 --> 00:25:26.000
mode -- the only note that's different from 

00:25:26.000 --> 00:25:28.000
the usual F-major scale. And I want you 

00:25:28.000 --> 00:25:30.000
to tell me which note is the peculiar 

00:25:30.000 --> 00:25:32.000
one, by clapping the second 

