as if a wrong note were 

00:26:14.000 --> 00:26:17.000
being played on purpose. And many 

00:26:17.000 --> 00:26:19.000
20th century composers have taken 

00:26:19.000 --> 00:26:22.000
advantage of this Lydian mode to get 

00:26:22.000 --> 00:26:25.000
comic effects. For instance, Prokofieff, in his 

00:26:25.000 --> 00:26:28.000
music for the comedy-film "Lieutenant 

